---
// Difference component — Phase D
---

<section id="difference" class="difference" data-animate>
  <div class="difference__container">
    <span class="difference__overline">WHY REYNA HOUSE</span>

    <h2 class="difference__headline">
      Your Website Should Be Yours.<br />
      Not Rented. Not Held Hostage. Yours.
    </h2>

    <div class="difference__body">
      <p>When you sign up with Wix or Squarespace, you don't own your website. You're renting it. The day you stop paying, it disappears.</p>
      <p>We build your site in clean code. You get the files. You get the domain. You get the hosting. It's yours. Like your truck. Like your tools.</p>
      <p>If you never want to talk to us again after we hand it over — that's your right. But most of our clients come back. Because once you see what a real website does for your business, you want more.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="difference__cards">
      <!-- Left Card — Wix / Squarespace -->
      <div class="difference__card difference__card--wix">
        <div class="difference__card-header difference__card-header--wix">
          Wix / Squarespace
        </div>
        <ul class="difference__list">
          <li class="difference__list-item difference__list-item--negative">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <line x1="4" y1="4" x2="12" y2="12" stroke="#cc4444" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="4" x2="4" y2="12" stroke="#cc4444" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
            <span>You rent it</span>
          </li>
          <li class="difference__list-item difference__list-item--negative">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <line x1="4" y1="4" x2="12" y2="12" stroke="#cc4444" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="4" x2="4" y2="12" stroke="#cc4444" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Stop paying, it disappears</span>
          </li>
          <li class="difference__list-item difference__list-item--negative">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <line x1="4" y1="4" x2="12" y2="12" stroke="#cc4444" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="4" x2="4" y2="12" stroke="#cc4444" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Cookie-cutter templates</span>
          </li>
          <li class="difference__list-item difference__list-item--negative">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <line x1="4" y1="4" x2="12" y2="12" stroke="#cc4444" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="4" x2="4" y2="12" stroke="#cc4444" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
            <span>No code access</span>
          </li>
          <li class="difference__list-item difference__list-item--negative">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <line x1="4" y1="4" x2="12" y2="12" stroke="#cc4444" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="4" x2="4" y2="12" stroke="#cc4444" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Hidden fees</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Card — Reyna House AI -->
      <div class="difference__card difference__card--reyna">
        <div class="difference__card-header difference__card-header--reyna">
          Reyna House AI
        </div>
        <ul class="difference__list">
          <li class="difference__list-item difference__list-item--positive">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <polyline points="3,8 6.5,11.5 13,4.5" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            <span>You own it</span>
          </li>
          <li class="difference__list-item difference__list-item--positive">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <polyline points="3,8 6.5,11.5 13,4.5" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Yours forever</span>
          </li>
          <li class="difference__list-item difference__list-item--positive">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <polyline points="3,8 6.5,11.5 13,4.5" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Built for your business</span>
          </li>
          <li class="difference__list-item difference__list-item--positive">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <polyline points="3,8 6.5,11.5 13,4.5" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Full code on GitHub</span>
          </li>
          <li class="difference__list-item difference__list-item--positive">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <polyline points="3,8 6.5,11.5 13,4.5" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Flat rate, no surprises</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .difference {
    background-color: var(--navy);
    padding: 100px 24px;
  }

  .difference__container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .difference__overline {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    color: var(--copper);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .difference__headline {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .difference__body {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 56px;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .difference__body p {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .difference__cards {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .difference__card {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 420px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Wix card — de-emphasized */
  .difference__card--wix {
    background: #2a2a2a;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .difference__card-header {
    padding: 16px 24px;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .difference__card-header--wix {
    background: #555;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  /* Reyna card — emphasized */
  .difference__card--reyna {
    background: #1a2a1a;
    border: 2px solid var(--gold);
  }

  .difference__card-header--reyna {
    background: var(--copper);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .difference__list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 20px 24px;
  }

  .difference__list-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 12px 0;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(191, 169, 132, 0.15);
  }

  .difference__list-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .difference__list-item--negative span {
    color: var(--tan);
  }

  .difference__list-item--positive span {
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .difference__list-item svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .difference__cards {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .difference__card {
      max-width: 100%;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .difference__body {
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
